@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cimedp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(0.10)
    v2 = (v2 - wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.10)))
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.39 * v0 + 0.43) / (v2 + 0.67 - v2 + 0.85)) / (wp.exp(v1 + 0.53) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.96)))
    v0 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.82 + v0 + 0.01)) / (wp.abs(v0 + 0.60) - 0.03))
    data[tid] = v0
